assertor.title: QualWeb
assertor.description: QualWeb is an automatic accessibility evaluator for webpages.

test.title: Orientation of the page is not restricted using CSS transform property
test.description: This rule checks that page content is not restricted to either landscape or portrait orientation using CSS transform property.

result.description: A page where CSS transform property has rotate transform function conditionally applied on the orientation media feature which restricts the element to landscape orientation.
